ActIndian Act
SubjectTsuu T’ina Nation, Alberta ** Transfer **
PrecisOrder (1) consenting to the exercise of the power of the Province of Alberta to take 428.167 hectares (1,058 acres) of lands in TSUU T’INA NATION RESERVE NO. 145; and (2) authorizing, in lieu of such taking, the transfer of administration and control of these lands.
